        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"contents\": [\n    {\n      \"parts\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \"Create a stunning, professional Facebook social media graphic for the topic: \\\"{{$json.title}}\\\"\\n\\n🎨 DESIGN STYLE:\\n- Style: Modern graphic design with bold visual hierarchy\\n- Mood: {{$json.mood || 'Vibrant and engaging'}}\\n- Color Palette: Use rich, complementary colors that pop on Facebook feeds — deep gradients, bold accents, clean backgrounds\\n- Typography feel: Even without text, design should feel editorial and structured\\n- Visual theme: {{$json.theme || 'Professional and contemporary'}}\\n\\n📐 COMPOSITION & LAYOUT:\\n- Format: Square (1:1) or landscape (1.91:1) optimized for Facebook feed\\n- Use the rule of thirds for visual balance\\n- Strong focal point that immediately draws the eye\\n- Negative space used intentionally for breathing room\\n- Depth and dimension using shadows, gradients, or layered elements\\n\\n🖼️ VISUAL ELEMENTS:\\n- Include relevant symbolic imagery or abstract shapes that represent: {{$json.title}}\\n- Category/Industry: {{$json.category || 'General Business'}}\\n- Use: geometric patterns, flowing lines, or organic shapes as design elements\\n- Lighting: Cinematic or studio-quality lighting effect\\n- Textures: Subtle paper, metal, glass, or digital textures to add richness\\n\\n✨ QUALITY STANDARDS:\\n- Ultra high resolution, print-ready quality\\n- NO text overlays, NO watermarks, NO logos\\n- Clean edges, professional finish\\n- Pixel-perfect sharpness\\n- Colors vibrant enough to stand out in a busy social media feed\\n\\n🚫 AVOID:\\n- Cluttered or busy compositions\\n- Stock photo clichés\\n- Dull or muted color schemes\\n- Distorted proportions\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"generationConfig\": {\n    \"temperature\": 0.85,\n    \"topK\": 50,\n    \"topP\": 0.97,\n    \"maxOutputTokens\": 8192,\n    \"candidateCount\": 1\n  }\n}",
        "options": {}
      },
